e":"2020-02-21T02:20:51.000Z","msg":"新天地耶穌教證據帳幕聖殿（韓語：신천지예수교_증거장막성전，Shincheonji, Church of Jesus, the Temple of the Tabernacle of the Testimony），簡稱是新天地耶穌教會或是新天地，新天新地，是由李萬熙於1984年3月14日在韓國創建的新宗教團體，據稱有超過120,000名信徒[1]。<br />\n<br />\n新天地是一個有爭議性的組織，並經常被人指控為邪教團體[2][3][4]，或是基督教異端[5]。<br />\n新天地的信徒相信創始人李萬熙是耶穌的轉世，或是耶穌所派的使者[6]。新天地宣稱聖經中充滿著隱喻，只有創始人李萬熙可以看懂和解釋。[7]<br />\n在創立新天地之前，其創始人李萬熙是宗教團體Olive Tree（英語：Olive Tree (religious movement)）的成員。[8]<br />\n2016年11月，英格蘭教會向約500個教區發出正式警告，要求它們警惕新天地的附屬組織Parachristo的活動。[9]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%96%B0%E5%A4%A9%E5%9C%B0%E8%80%B6%E7%A8%A3%E6%95%99%E8%AF%81%E6%8D%AE%E5%B8%90%E5%B9%95%E5%9C%A3%E6%AE%BF%E6%95%99%E4%BC%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%2580%25B6%25E7%25A8%25A3%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%25AF%2581%25E6%258D%25AE%25E5%25B8%2590%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%259C%25A3%25E6%25AE%25BF%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25BC%259A&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqFwwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=2271e216\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%96%B0%E5%A4%A9%E5%9C%B0%E8%80%B6%E7%A8%A3%E6%95%99%E8%AF%81%E6%8D%AE%E5%B8%90%E5%B9%95%E5%9C%A3%E6%AE%BF%E6%95%99%E4%BC%9A</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T03:17:18.000Z","msg":"Matthew 24:5 <br />\nFor many shall come in my name, saying, I am the Christ; and shall lead many astray.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90c3338a47c0dbd567b62ac68650f65ba95ac52","tid":1889982,"uid":49004,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"18c321430d8ee7f055dac15ace4950c54ae22ca2","tid":1889982,"uid":78392,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"a9578868dc75988778eac48339ad0773bc957d21","tid":1889982,"uid":134683,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1176268cdf8e3eb7b03d5681a7af28552902e25e","tid":1889982,"uid":39381,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T02:22:07.000Z","msg":"日韓特別多邪教<img src=\"/asset