By":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T02:18:31.000Z","msg":"【南韓疫情】異端教會禁口罩 造就超級傳播者出現<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2569030/?lcc=an\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2569030%2F%3Flcc%3Dan&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqFwwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=4d2c5aae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2569030/?lcc=an</a><br />\n<br />\n南韓新型冠狀病毒肺炎新冠肺炎（武漢肺炎）疫情未止，今日更新增20宗新冠肺炎確診個案，其中至少15人曾與大邱市昨日確診的超級傳播者接觸。韓媒報道指，該超級傳播者所前往的新天地教會，禮拜時不准信徒戴著口罩，或是造成大批信徒感染新冠肺炎的原因。<br />\n<br />\n南韓《韓國日報》報道指，該名61歲的女子分別在2月9日、2月16日前往大邱一間新天地教會禮拜，患者在教會停留約2個小時，其後有多名信徒確診。<br />\n<br />\n南韓CBS廣播公司報道指，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新天地教會要求信徒在禮拜時穿著特定的服裝，亦不准信徒戴著口罩，故此即使教會內聚集逾500人，都幾乎沒有人戴口罩。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n報道又指，該批曾與超級傳播者接觸的患者都是<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">年約30歲至60歲，大多都是女性。而原因是新天地教會的禮拜座位是按性別和年齡區分。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n報道指，而在<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">禮拜之後，該批婦女大多會各自分享事先在家準備的食物。在狹小的空間近2小時，逾500人沒有戴上口罩面對面地說話、進食，絕對有感染病毒的風險。</span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T03:54:07.000Z","msg":"連續２日過５０單。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asia/covid19-south-korea-52-new-coronavirus-cases-total-156-12456158\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.channelnewsasia.com%2Fnews%2Fasia%2Fcovid19-south-korea-52-new-coronavirus-cases-total-156-12456158&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqFwwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=f2d81aa5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asia/covid19-south-korea-52-new-coronavirus-cases-total-156-12456158</a><br />\n<br />\nSEOUL: South Korea reported <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">52</span> new confirmed cases of the coronavirus on Friday (Feb 21), taking the national total to <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">156</span>, with the majority in Daegu（大邱）, the country's fourth-largest city.<br />\n<br />\nUpdated: 21 Feb 2020 10:44AM"},{"pid":"4760fbad712e4fdb4c1714b62d8f1d49bd4511f1","tid":1889982,"u